'''Synstone''' was a substance used for building construction on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. [[Ben Kenobi's home/Legends|Ben Kenobi's hut]] was made out of it. It was made from pulverized rock mixed with a dissolvant and sprayed onto a frame, where it would harden into the building needed.

